  <div class="page-header">
    <h1>How To Mine</h1>
  </div>
  <p class="lead">In order to mine on this pool you need to have an
    <a href="https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=1433925.0" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Claymore's Dual Ethereum Miner</a> installation
    pointed to<br/><code>{{config.StratumHost}}:{{config.StratumPort}}</code>
  </p>
  <dl class="dl-horizontal">
    <dt>YOUR_EOSC_ADDRESS</dt>
    <dd>This is your address for payouts, generate one at <a href="https://myetherwallet.com" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">MyEtherWallet</a> or <a href="https://github.com/eosclassic/mist/releases" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">EOSC Desktop Wallet</a>.<br/>
      <strong>Example:</strong> <code>0x63fc6bf24415D69FD03B4eABa425A4fB3310ccc7</code>.
    </dd>
    <dt>RIG_ID</dt>
    <dd>
      ID of your farm to distinguish it from your other rig. If you have just one rig, feel free to omit this param.
      This param must be short alphanumeric string with optional dashes and underscores.<br/>
      <strong>Example:</strong> <code>rig-1</code>
    </dd>
  </dl>
  <p>
    <strong>Full example:</strong>
    <code>EthDcrMiner64.exe -epool {{config.StratumHost}}:{{config.StratumPort}} -ewal 0x63fc6bf24415D69FD03B4eABa425A4fB3310ccc7 -eworker myfarm -epsw x -allcoins 1 -mode 1</code>.
  </p>

  <h4>Advice</h4>
  <p>CPU mining is not recommended.</p>
